I conducted a thorough analysis

00:05:13.060 --> 00:05:19.240
from the 1920's to the 1980's as
it relates to the rhetoric exposed

00:05:19.240 --> 00:05:23.290
in advertisements mostly
graphic of pads and tampons

00:05:23.290 --> 00:05:28.200 position:56%
in the social context where these
images circulated in both countries.

00:05:28.200 --> 00:05:31.320
I review more than 400 ads.

00:05:31.320 --> 00:05:34.530
I also looked for the
most significant patterns,

00:05:34.530 --> 00:05:37.230
the educational materials
produced by the main companies

00:05:37.230 --> 00:05:40.720
