the experiences of women

00:05:40.720 --> 00:05:43.230
about the menstrual body,
as well as the meaning

00:05:43.230 --> 00:05:46.410
that these modern technologies
represented for those who live

00:05:46.410 --> 00:05:50.320
through the transition from
the rag, cloths and cotton

00:05:50.320 --> 00:05:55.670
