00:14:33.900 --> 00:14:37.620
at different levels by letting
them perform a socially acceptable

00:14:37.620 --> 00:14:39.750
feminine body before others

00:14:39.750 --> 00:14:42.800
and remain active every
day of the month.

00:14:42.800 --> 00:14:47.500
