how they did all that.

00:14:47.500 --> 00:14:51.430
And the answer is by normalizing
the menstrual body gradually

00:14:51.430 --> 00:14:55.330
under the idea of a feminine
body for which menstruation was

00:14:55.330 --> 00:15:00.420
under control the processing
played two major tactics.

00:15:00.420 --> 00:15:05.940
The first one and most fundamental
was effectively conceding not

00:15:05.940 --> 00:15:10.010
suppressing all the evident
traces of menstruation,

00:15:10.010 --> 00:15:13.100
even its consideration of abject

00:15:13.100 --> 00:15:17.040
by letting women be more
productive every day of the month.

00:15:17.040 --> 00:15:22.210
This meant a decreased anxiety
related to the subservience

00:15:22.210 --> 00:15:26.540
over the evidence of the
existence of a menstrual body.

00:15:26.540 --> 00:15:30.150
Manufacturing of disposable pads
and tampons helped women avoid

00:15:30.150 --> 00:15:34.560
in a more efficient way the sting,
the smell, the visual traces

00:15:34.560 --> 00:15:38.270
of a homemade pad and
also they were disposable.

00:15:38.270 --> 00:15:42.130 position:56%
So women did not have to worry about
finding a place to hide the product

00:15:42.130 --> 00:15:47.690
for store it or where to dry
them without being seen by men.

00:15:47.690 --> 00:15:52.100
And finally the improvements in
terms of comfort made women get rid

00:15:52.100 --> 00:15:55.810
of the permanent self-awareness
about the menstrual condition

00:15:55.810 --> 00:15:58.420
without suppressing menstruation.

00:15:58.420 --> 00:16:02.780
